    • canShowGlobalWorkloadStats

      public boolean canShowGlobalWorkloadStats()
      Returns true if the the current user can view global workload statistics. This is based on whether the system has been configured to allow this (the GroupSummaryShowUserGlobalWorkloadStats has been set to true) and the user has the corrrect permissions to do so (viewworkload permmission).
      Returns:
      true if the user meets the criteria to view global workload statistics.
